node.text:
Here is a little video I did for my @comptrain.co family that I want to share with all of you guys about what confidence means to me ✨☺️🙌🏼☀️
-
It’s not the kind of confidence where “I know I am the best” - that is something I can never be sure of & something that is outside my control.
-
It’s the kind of confidence that I know I am as prepared as I can be in a given moment. It’s the kind of confidence I TRUST that I can handle anything that comes my way. It’s the kind I have to work my ass off every single day to EARN that confidence & only I will know if I truly did that.
-
It’s the kind of you confidence I have to EARN for myself. So today: EARN YOURS 💥👊🏼🥰 #BeTheBestYOU

node.text: Sundays are for relaxation & catchup ☕️🤍☺️💻✨ Got most of my computer work done this morning & then this afternoon was aaaaaaall for the mind + body: 1hr easy bike, 30 min sauna (currently reading the book of JOY. So so good) & then sat in the outdoor hot tubs. Ready for a new training week to hit tomorrow! xxx

node.text:
Just caught my very first salmon at our summerhouse with my grandpa! ✨☺️🎣❤️ Moments don’t get much more special than this.

Afi has been fishing in this river for 70 years now & yesterday I got to be guided by him while I reeled in my first catch. I love that I get to learn from him & experience this with him. It was such a proud moment for him & a very special one to me ✨

node.text:
Cheers to our best girl ✨🥂❤️☀️🥰 My little sister is getting MARRIED next weekend! @hannahdavidsdottir 

Loved getting to celebrate her & this new chapter in her life with all of her favorite women! An incredible day together that we got to end with a celebration at our favorite restaurant in Reykjavik.

Thank you @grillmarkadurinn (“The Grill Market”) for THE WARMEST, best & most delicious welcomes! ✨😋 .. swipe for my new favorite salad: duck salad. xxx
